Subject: drm/i2c: tda998x: get rid of private fill_modes function
Git-commit: a3d335f5de7cdd714737a9f8bdcc7b205b0f8d5e
Patch-mainline: v4.19-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

We can achieve the same effect via the get_modes() method, rather than
wrapping the fill_modes helper.

